  <chapter>
    <title>Xapian-GLib</title>

    <refsect2 id="overview">
      <para>
        Xapian-GLib is a library providing a C API to the
        Xapian library, using GObject to map to Xapian classes.
        Using Xapian-GLib makes it possible to access, create, and
        query Xapian databases with C and other various other
        programming languages that can consume the GObject
        introspection data.
      </para>
    </refsect2>

